# Rust
/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.orig

# Yard runtime state. This repo now self-hosts Yard: we TRACK the .agents/
# config (yardlet.yaml, *-policy.yaml, workers.yaml, skills/) and ignore the
# per-run operational artifacts below. The work queue is runtime state, not
# config, so THIS repo gitignores it to keep dogfood runs out of the product
# tree (other repos may choose to track their own queue).
/.agents/runs/
/.agents/checkpoints/
/.agents/handoffs/
/.agents/telemetry/
/.agents/intents/
/.agents/intent-contract.yaml
/.agents/work-queue.yaml

# Personal / per-machine harness files
*.local
.claude/settings.local.json
.codex/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
/.agents/worktrees/

# internal planning docs (kept local, not public)
docs/yardlet-final-plan.md
docs/yardlet-roadmap.md
docs/yardlet-queue-ownership-design.md
